## Limitations

The report is limited by the availability of recent and comprehensive data on media practices. The selected sources provide a snapshot but may not cover all aspects of media responsibility. Additionally, the analysis is constrained by the subjective nature of ethical considerations and the varying standards across different media platforms and regions. Further research could provide a more detailed understanding of the media's role and responsibilities in different contexts.

